# Inventory Management System — Implementation Plan

Full-stack inventory management dashboard with **Next.js** (frontend), **NestJS** (backend), and **SQLite** (local `database.sqlite`).

## Project Structure

```
e:\allen-task2\
├── backend/          # NestJS API
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── auth/     # Login & Signup
│   │   ├── products/ # Products CRUD
│   │   ├── customers/# Customers CRUD
│   │   ├── orders/   # Orders CRUD
│   │   ├── seed/     # Database seeder
│   │   └── entities/ # TypeORM entities
│   └── ...
├── frontend/         # Next.js App
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── login/    # Login/Signup page
│   │   ├── dashboard/# Main dashboard
│   │   ├── products/ # Products management
│   │   ├── customers/# Customers management
│   │   └── orders/   # Orders management
│   └── ...
```

---

## Database Schema (SQLite — TypeORM)

Database file: `backend/database.sqlite` (auto-created on first run via TypeORM `synchronize: true`).

### Tables

| Table | Columns |
|-------|---------|
| **users** | `id` (PK, auto), `name`, `email` (unique), `password`, `role` (default: 'admin'), `createdAt` |
| **products** | `id` (PK, auto), `name`, `sku` (unique), `category`, `price`, `quantity`, `description`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt` |
| **customers** | `id` (PK, auto), `name`, `email` (unique), `phone`, `address`, `city`, `createdAt` |
| **orders** | `id` (PK, auto), `orderNumber` (unique), `customerId` (FK → customers), `productId` (FK → products), `quantity`, `totalPrice`, `status` (pending/completed/cancelled), `createdAt` |

### Seed Data
- **5 users** (admin accounts)
- **15 products** (electronics, clothing, accessories)
- **10 customers** 
- **20 orders** (linked to customers & products)

---

## Backend — NestJS API

### Modules & Endpoints

#### Auth Module (`/api/auth`)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/signup` | Register new user (name, email, password) |
| POST | `/login` | Login (email, password) — returns user object, no JWT |

#### Products Module (`/api/products`)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/` | List all products (with search & pagination) |
| GET | `/:id` | Get single product |
| POST | `/` | Create product |
| PATCH | `/:id` | Update product |
| DELETE | `/:id` | Delete product |

#### Customers Module (`/api/customers`)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/` | List all customers (with search & pagination) |
| GET | `/:id` | Get single customer |
| POST | `/` | Create customer |
| PATCH | `/:id` | Update customer |
| DELETE | `/:id` | Delete customer |

#### Orders Module (`/api/orders`)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/` | List all orders (with relations, search & pagination) |
| GET | `/:id` | Get single order |
| POST | `/` | Create order |
| PATCH | `/:id` | Update order |
| DELETE | `/:id` | Delete order |

#### Seed Module
- `GET /api/seed` — Runs seeder to populate database with initial data

---

## Frontend — Next.js (App Router)

### Design System
- **Theme**: Dark professional dashboard (dark navy/slate background, neon blue accents, white text)
- **Font**: Inter (Google Fonts)
- **Cards**: Glassmorphism effect with subtle borders
- **Animations**: Smooth transitions, hover effects, micro-animations on stats
- **Fully responsive**: Mobile-first, sidebar collapses to hamburger menu

### Pages

#### 1. Login/Signup Page (`/login`)
- Single page with **tab toggle** between Login & Signup
- Clean centered card with glassmorphism
- Form fields: Name (signup), Email, Password
- Auto-redirect to dashboard on success

#### 2. Dashboard (`/dashboard`)
- **Sidebar**: Navigation links (Dashboard, Products, Customers, Orders, Logout)
- **Header**: Welcome message, user avatar placeholder
- **Stats Cards**: Total Products, Total Customers, Total Orders, Revenue
- **Recent Orders Table**: Last 5 orders
- **Quick Action Buttons**: Add Product, Add Customer, New Order

#### 3. Products Page (`/products`)
- **Data Table**: Name, SKU, Category, Price, Quantity, Actions (Edit/Delete)
- **Search bar** + **Add Product button**
- **Modal**: Add/Edit product form
- **Delete confirmation** dialog

#### 4. Customers Page (`/customers`)
- **Data Table**: Name, Email, Phone, City, Actions (Edit/Delete)
- **Search bar** + **Add Customer button**
- **Modal**: Add/Edit customer form
- **Delete confirmation** dialog

#### 5. Orders Page (`/orders`)
- **Data Table**: Order #, Customer, Product, Qty, Total, Status, Actions
- **Search bar** + **New Order button**
- **Modal**: Create/Edit order (dropdowns for customer & product)
- **Status badge** (color-coded: green/yellow/red)

